OL,3,CJersey Zoo members call for board to
OL,4,Cbe ousted amid welfare allegations
OL,6,FMore than 100 members of Durrell's
OL,7,FWildlife Conservation Trust have
OL,8,Fcalled for Zoo's board of trustees to
OL,9,Fbe ousted amid allegations about the
OL,10,Fpoor treatment of animals, staff
OL,11,Fbullying and concerns over the
OL,12,Fdirection of the charity.
OL,14,FSome of the allegations shared with
OL,15,FITV News include that nocturnal
OL,16,Fanimals were put on show in the
OL,17,Fdaytime and woken up for cuddles on
OL,18,FVIP visits, and goats were put in an
OL,19,Finappropriate environment that led to
OL,20,Fthem getting footrot.
