OL,3,CJersey Zoo members call for board to
OL,4,Cbe ousted amid welfare allegations
OL,6,FIn response, Matthew Hatchwell, Chair
OL,7,Fof Trustees at Durrell, says: "Animal
OL,8,Fwelfare is and has always been
OL,9,FDurrell's priority.
OL,11,F"We have a zero-tolerance policy on
OL,12,Fbullying. The picture that's being
OL,13,Fpainted to my mind, as far as it's
OL,14,Fpossible to tell as a Trustee, is not
OL,15,Frepresentative of the attitude to the
OL,16,FTrust among employees as a whole."
