OL,3,CJersey Zoo members call for board to
OL,4,Cbe ousted amid welfare allegations
OL,6,FMembers have collected enough
OL,7,Fsignatures for an 'Extraordinary
OL,8,FGeneral Meeting' which could see
OL,9,Fsenior figures pushed out and prompt
OL,10,Fan investigation into the running of
OL,11,Fthe zoo.
OL,13,FMr Hatchwell adds: "The requisition
OL,14,Ffor an Extraordinary General Meeting
OL,15,Fhas come from less than 1% of the
OL,16,Fmembership, we don't believe that
OL,17,Fthey're representative of the 20,000
OL,18,For so members that we have around the
OL,19,Fworld and we welcome the opportunity
OL,20,Fto speak to both the supporters and
OL,21,Fthe critics when the time comes."
