OL,3,CJersey Zoo members call for board to
OL,4,Cbe ousted amid welfare allegations
OL,6,FAllegations of a in August 2023 saw
OL,7,Fthe board issue a statement saying it
OL,8,F"deplores malicious or ill-founded
OL,9,Faccusations" and that a committee
OL,10,Fincluding independent experts had no
OL,11,Fconcerns.
OL,13,FAddressing the issues raised over
OL,14,Frecent months through a public
OL,15,Fstatement, Honorary Director Lee
OL,16,FDurrell says: "The concerns raised,
OL,17,Falbeit well-intentioned, have infused
OL,18,Fthe debates with diverse agendas and
OL,19,Funyielding opinions, which have had a
OL,20,Fnegative impact on stability and
OL,21,Fmorale at Jersey Zoo.
