OL,6,F"I therefore ask those people to stop
OL,7,Fusing Gerald Durrell's name and legacy
OL,8,Fto justify their criticisms. Whatever
OL,9,Foutcomes they seek, Gerry would have
OL,10,Fbeen deeply saddened to see the damage
OL,11,Fdone to the Trust to which he gave his
OL,12,Fname and dedicated his life."
